productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lular has one of these. She works as a cake decorator and she says it looks ragged.
My neighbor Karly has one of these. She works as a gambler and she says it looks tall.
i use it daily when i'm in my outhouse.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
This Assistant works quite well. It pointedly improves my golf by a lot.
